  "description": "A vibrant coastal scene features waves crashing onto a sandy beach under a bright blue sky with scattered white clouds. The waves are in varying stages of breaking, creating white foam and splashes as they roll towards the shore. The water is a mix of deep blue and turquoise, becoming frothy and white as it approaches the beach. In the distant background, a coastline with rolling hills and a faint hint of vegetation is visible. The lighting is bright and sunny, creating a sense of warmth and tranquility. The beach is dark grey.",
